data.description: Welcome to this gorgeous LAKEFRONT HOME in the master-planned community of LAGO MAR. There are so many upgrades to this 2022 built 4-sided brick home including stunning granite counters in the kitchen that have veins throughout with incredible movement. 3 good size bedrooms & 2 full baths maximizes the space in this sweet 1 story home. Fridge, washer & dryer included. Updates: front & back storm doors plus gutters added in February 2023. Solar screens added to all exterior windows in March 2023. 6 zone sprinkler sytem, & fresh interior & exterior paint, added in May of 2023, plus all new frontyard sod in July. Enjoy a staycation whenever you're home!! Lago Mar is known for it's huge lagoon with crystal clear blue waters & white sand beaches with lagoon-side alfresco dining on the beach boardwalk from Blue Lagoon Bar & Grill. Resort-style Recreation Center boasts clubhouse, pool, gym, playground & greenspace. This is a golf cart friendly community. New elementary school is coming soon.
